Title: Subterraneans (2)
Plot: The team discover the brutally murdered body of a man in the same cellar that the businessman was held hostage in. While investigating the two victims, the team find an unlikely suspect. They're positive of his connection to the murders, but need to collect the evidence to prove it.
ParentalRatingReason: Contains violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Ronan Vibert,  Nicola Stephenson,  Toby Stephens,  Jake   Seage,  Mark Monero,  Gareth  Mason,  Francis Magee,  Kelly Harrison,  Frank Harper,  Laurie  Hagen,  Ayesha Dharker,  Alexis Conran,  Luke  Booker-Morel
